lead_paragraph: Joonas Donskoi wasn't even born when the San Jose Sharks started in 1991 and hadn't taken part in any of a series of playoff disappointments that haunted the franchise over the years.

headline.print_headline: Donskoi's OT Goal Gives Sharks 3-2 Win Over Pens in Game 3
